  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8107524/" class="title-link">老子讲的道便是霎哈嘉瑜伽中的灵量</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8107524"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42033941-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-30"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-30 11:19:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8107524_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  老子所讲的道，便是霎哈嘉瑜伽中的灵性的力量（通常也简称为灵量）。 “老子所讲的「道」，其实就是我们讲的昆达里尼（ Kundalini），灵性的能量。老子是个诗人，他所描述的方式是很隐晦，很微妙的。许多人也许觉得老子的道很难明白，可是这个道在世界各地均受到尊崇，而且人们...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8107524_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8107524_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





